narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: you don't learn much new grammar. instead, you refine your speaking and vocabulary skills so that you can write better essays and speak more fluidly (you do some grammar review, which is also helpful)
You will need to work but it is worth it.
I would recommend G 140 to another student who is interested in improving his/her German language skills.
